metadata.name: adidas /// Blue Pass
metadata.description:
Blue Pass is soulbound (a non-transferable token) and cannot be traded. Once the time is right, only the holders of this token will be able to activate it for another (more tradable token) in the future.

Head to [discord.gg/adidas](https://discord.gg/adidas) for more details. View [terms and conditions](https://a.did.as/collect_tc
